    <briefdescription>
<para>Abstract interface for processing spawn rules into spawn plans. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1spawn_1_1scheduling_1_1RuleProcessor" kindref="compound">RuleProcessor</ref> defines the contract for evaluating a single spawn rule and producing a <ref refid="structhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1spawn_1_1scheduling_1_1SpawnPlan" kindref="compound">SpawnPlan</ref>. This abstraction allows different processing strategies to be plugged into schedulers.</para>
<para>## Responsibilities</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Retrieve pool and profile information from the game world</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Update the rule&apos;s state (timers, counts)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Evaluate the rule&apos;s conditions</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Produce a <ref refid="structhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1spawn_1_1scheduling_1_1SpawnPlan" kindref="compound">SpawnPlan</ref> if conditions are met</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1spawn_1_1scheduling_1_1DefaultRuleProcessor" kindref="compound">DefaultRuleProcessor</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1spawn_1_1scheduling_1_1SpawnScheduler" kindref="compound">SpawnScheduler</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1spawn_1_1policy_1_1SpawnRule" kindref="compound">SpawnRule</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
